msgid "For Bloggers and Publishers"
msgstr ""

#: webmcp-toolkit-pro/webmcp-toolkit-pro.php:225
msgid ""
"Bloggers can use WebMCP Toolkit PRO to guide AI readers toward search, "
"article details, comments, and accurate site context. This is useful for "
"content-heavy sites where assistants need to find posts, summarize topics, "
"or help visitors navigate archives."
